mkdir - create directories
Executable: /bin/mkdir.sh
Alias: mkdir

DESCRIPTION
  Creates one or more
  directories.

USAGE
  mkdir <dir> [dir...]
  mkdir -p <dir> [dir...]

OPTIONS
  -p
    Treat existing
    directories as success.

NOTES
  Parent directories are
  created automatically by
  the CC: Tweaked filesystem
  API.
